<br />
<div style="text-align: center;" class="mycode_align"><img src="https://www.upload.ee/image/10251690/POI03.png" loading="lazy"  alt="[Image: POI03.png]" class="mycode_img" /></div>
<br />
<div style="text-align: center;" class="mycode_align"><img src="https://www.upload.ee/image/10251677/POI04.png" loading="lazy"  alt="[Image: POI04.png]" class="mycode_img" /></div>]]></content>
